rows.label: qst701508_msg0001
rows.name:
Haa haa... I thought
my time had come...

rows.label: qst701508_msg0002
rows.name: Is it okay for you to be standing?

rows.label: qst701508_msg0004
rows.name:
No need to worry. Thanks to
you, I feel much better.

rows.label: qst701508_msg0005
rows.name:
I've been having these attacks
sometimes. But I'll be fine
with a little rest.

rows.label: qst701508_msg0006
rows.name:
...I'd love for you to rest,
but you have a guest.

rows.label: qst701508_msg0007
rows.name: A guest? Ah, a guest at the inn?

rows.label: qst701508_msg0008
rows.name:
That's not good! I must have kept
them waiting. I have to hurry.

rows.label: qst701508_msg0009
rows.name: Eh!? It's dangerous to go alone!

rows.label: qst701508_msg0010
rows.name: Laura! ...I guess it can't be helped.

rows.label: qst701508_msg0011
rows.name: Wadatsumi, come with me, just in case.

rows.label: qst701508_msg0013
rows.name:
I can't believe he was
collapsed just a moment ago.

rows.label: qst701508_msg0014
rows.name:
He's young at heart. That
in itself is a good thing.

rows.label: qst701508_msg0016
rows.name:
In any case, we can
only watch over them.
